title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On February 23, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190060001 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds. Any previously assigned priority or processing date is no longer applicable. If you wish to still pursue the benefit, you must file a new application or petition and submit a new fee filing fee. title: Petition/Application Was Rejected For Insufficient Funds
body: On February 23, 2021, we rejected your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190060138 because your filing fee was returned by your financial institution for insufficient funds.
